eavactiverecord Change Log
==========================

Version 1.0.3 November 19, 2014
-------------------------------
- Bug #11: The method EavActiveRecord::saveWithEavAttributes() failed
- Enh #12: Add type conversion for some string values

Version 1.0.3 November 4, 2014
------------------------------
- Bug #7: The settings are not available for the bundled validator CExistValidator
- Bug #8: The class EavAttributeExtended should use composition instead of inheritance
- Bug #9: array_combine(): Both parameters should have an equal number of elements
- New: Added MoneyDataType, NumericDataType

Version 1.0.2 October 20, 2014
------------------------------
- New: Added the new method EavAttribute::getPossibleValues()
- New: Added the new method EavAttribute::setPossibleValues()
- New: Added the new class CountValidator
- New: Added the new class MultivaluedValidator
- New: Added the GUI module for user interaction (front-end module) based on the extension API
- New: Added support for validators that validate multivalued attributes

Version 1.0.1  October 8, 2014
------------------------------
- Bug #2: Output EAV-attributes in wrong order.
- Bug #3: Checking actual value of the entity's primary key attribute.
- Bug #4: EavActiveRecord::updateWithEavAttributes(), EavActiveRecord::saveEavAttributes() perform an unexpected insert.
- New: Added the new method EavActiveRecord::saveEavAttributes()
- New: Added the new method EavValue::insertValue()
- New: Added the new method EavValue::updateEntityPrimaryKey()
- New: Added the new method EavSet::getEavAttributes()
- New: Added the new method EavSet::updateEavAttributeOrder()
- New: Added support for PostgreSQL
